# ESP32 module comparison

The toolkit has been tested with the following development boards, but any ESP32 should work:
|                         |   TTGO T8                                                                                                       |   NodeMCU                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |   WINGONEER TS V1.2                                                                     |
|-------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|   Tested board version  |   v1.7.1 is the latest version but it is not yet verified that this version has been tested with this project.  |   v4 is the latest and has been successfully tested. It is harder to find outside of Germany, but is reported to be better built than v2.                                                                                                                      |   v1.2 has been successfully tested.                                                    |
|   SD card               |   Yes                                                                                                           |   No                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |   Yes                                                                                   |
|   LCD display           |   No                                                                                                            |   No                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |   Yes                                                                                   |
|   Speakers              |   No                                                                                                            |   No                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |   Yes                                                                                   |
|   Processor             |   Unknown                                                                                                       |   Tensilica LX6 Dual-Core                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |   Unknown                                                                               |
|   Clock frequency       |   Unknown                                                                                                       |   240 MHz                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |   Unknown                                                                               |
|   RAM                   |   4MB PSRAM                                                                                                     |   512KB SRAM                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |   Unknown                                                                               |
|   Memory                |   4MB                                                                                                           |   4MB                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |   Unknown                                                                               |
|   Wireless standard     |   Unknown                                                                                                       |   802.11 b/g/n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |   Unknown                                                                               |
|   Bluetooth             |   Yes                                                                                                           |   Yes                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                         |   Yes                                                                                   |
|   Frequency             |   Unknown                                                                                                       |   2.4 GHz                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |   Unknown                                                                               |
|   Dimensions            |   63.3mm x 26.8mm x 4.7mm                                                                                       |   48mm x 26mm x 11.5mm                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |   Unknown                                                                               |
|   Operating voltage     |   Unknown                                                                                                       |   3.3V                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        |   Unknown                                                                               |
